# Business Context

## Project / Service Name
My projects

## What does this system do?
Brief description of the system's purpose and what data it processes.

## Critical Components
List the components that are most important to protect and why. Include physical id in brackets.

- **API Gateway (lvzpzw2ls1)**: Public-facing entry point. Handles all customer API requests.
- **Dispatches Lambda**: Core business logic. Processes tariff calculations with sensitive pricing data.
- **Valkey Cache**: Stores completed dispatch results. Contains customer-specific calculation outputs.

## Sensitive Data
What sensitive data flows through the system?

- Customer account identifiers
- Tariff calculation inputs/outputs (commercially sensitive)
- API authentication tokens

## Compliance / Regulatory Requirements
Any standards or regulations that apply (e.g. GDPR, PCI-DSS, SOC2).

- GDPR (customer data)

