## Trust Assumptions
What do we trust? What don't we trust?

- We trust: Internal VPC traffic between Lambda and Valkey
- We don't trust: Any traffic arriving at the API Gateway from the internet
- We don't trust: Developer access without MFA

## Known Gaps / Areas of Concern
Anything you already know is weak or needs attention.

- No WAF currently in front of API Gateway
- Jumpbox access controls need review
